&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Gusto’s Go To Market AI engineering team, including the recruitment, hiring, and empowerment of a world-class team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with AI Scientists and AI Product Managers to create a world where the sales motions run proactively and efficiently with AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead your engineering team to design, develop, and deploy AI-powered applications to enhance customer and advocate experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
