&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of client-facing experience - bonus points for exposure to healthcare, payroll, or a start-up environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empathetic and customer-centric: You care deeply about the customers you serve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and oral communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in problem solving, dealing with ambiguity, and cross-team communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated and comfortable working collaboratively and autonomously - excited about striving toward team and individual metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work throughout seasonal peaks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adap

