&lt;li&gt;Build repeatable, programmatic partnership motions (e.g., portfolio company programs, founder and operator education, marketplace or platform integrations)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the Tier 1 point of contact for a core group of high-impact ecosystem partners&lt;/li&gt;
